                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/c6b2492db5e3590f537e62d41855a4c6_997943773389044894.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Floral Sidewinder ",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ชนะโดยจำนวนตัวละครที่ถูกกำจัดต่ำกว่า 2 ตัว",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3234,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/c6b2492db5e3590f537e62d41855a4c6_997943773389044894.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Floral Sidewinder ",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "การต่อสู้อย่างจริงจัง",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "แนะนำด่าน",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"ไม่เป็นไร ฝีมือการเล่นของฉันก็พัฒนาขึ้นบ้างแล้วเหมือนกัน เข้ามาเลย!\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "[กฎพิเศษ] ในตอนเริ่ม \"Collei\" จะติดตั้งการ์ดพรสวรรค์ \"Floral Sidewinder\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ทีมของคู่ต่อสู้",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3189,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/ba092c866fbf6574b792b5e53eadf9ff_1210638388553983903.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Collei",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3182,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/6219bf1fb0b7c46b8ecf960443f737d5_1444721138988713800.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Xiangling",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3178,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/144837601/2c2d8a83c9a5a9a97531fee1491efa85_8342250375522902523.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Mona",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ปลดล็อกหลัง:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "มีเลเวลผู้เล่นถึง 7",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "สำเร็จเป้าหมายการท้าทาย Collei - เป็นมิตร 3 อัน",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "เป้าหมายการท้าทาย",
